javax.slee.profile
Interface ProfileSpecificationID

All Superinterfaces:
ComponentID
public interface ProfileSpecificationID
extends ComponentID

The ProfileSpecificationID interface is a marker interface implemented by every Java object that encapsulates profile specification component identity. A ProfileSpecificationID object is also known as a profile specification identifier.
